Global 10KV-33KV Gas Insulated Switchgears Market Insights
10KV-33KV Gas Insulated Switchgears Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

10KV-33KV Gas Insulated Switchgears Market Overview
The global 10KV-33KV Gas Insulated Switchgears (GIS) market is experiencing significant growth, with an expected market value of USD 5.6 billion in 2025, expanding at a CAGR of 8.1% from 2023 to 2025. GIS is being increasingly adopted due to its compact size, high efficiency, and enhanced safety features compared to air-insulated switchgear (AIS). The market is driven by the increasing demand for reliable power distribution systems, coupled with the growing emphasis on renewable energy integration. North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific are key regions contributing to the market growth, with substantial investments in infrastructure and smart grid projects. However, challenges such as high installation costs and the need for skilled professionals remain prevalent.

